app.title: Supplementary Materials
app.p: Steps of lipid autoxidation; Chromatograms of the 37 FAMEs; Chromatograms of the raw and roasted soybean flour prior to storage; and Chromatograms and tables of raw and roasted soybean flour packed in polyethylene and polypropylene film stored at refrigeration (4 °C), room temperature (20 °C), and high temperature (45 °C, as the accelerated condition) are available online.
